import React from 'react'
import { Center, Box, FormControl, Stack, Input, useColorMode, Button } from 'native-base'

export default function Home() {
    const {
        colorMode,
        toggleColorMode
      } = useColorMode()

  return <Box w="100%" bg={colorMode === 'dark' ? 'coolGray.800' : 'warmGray.50'}>
      <FormControl>
        <Stack mx="20">
        <Button onPress={toggleColorMode}>Toggle</Button>
          <FormControl.Label>Value A</FormControl.Label>
          <Input />
        </Stack>
      </FormControl>
      <FormControl>
        <Stack mx="20">
          <FormControl.Label>Value B</FormControl.Label>
          <Input />
        </Stack>
      </FormControl>
</Box>
}
